OL,5, One road in Wales now has eight speed  
OL,6, limit changes in less than two miles   
OL,7, following the switch to 20mph.         
OL,9,FThe A4222 in Aberthin, Vale of         
OL,10,FGlamorgan, includes stretches of 40mph 
OL,11,Fand 60mph in the space of 1.8 miles    
OL,12,F(2.9km).                               
OL,14,FIt follows Wales' default speed limit  
OL,15,Fdropping from 30mph to 20mph in        
OL,16,FSeptember.                             
OL,18,FOne 30mph stretch in the village just  
OL,19,Foutside Cowbridge is 520ft (160m) and  
OL,20,Feach new road sign costs #1,000 to fit.
